branchCategory.name: 10/11/12/21/22-CXS
branchCategory.description: <P>SMC's clean room version of the CXS dual rod cylinder is available in 6 bore sizes (6, 10, 16, 20, 25 and 32mm) with stroke lengths up to 100mm. It is suited for accurate pick-and-place applications or light duty material handling.  The CXSJ, compact, dual rod cylinder is available in 2 bore sizes (6mm and 10mm) with strokes up to 50mm.  Both the CXS and the CXSJ can be used with either reed or solid state switches. </P>
